Package: simpleos
Version: 1.0.0
Section: system
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6
Maintainer: SimpleOS Team <maintainer@simpleos.org>
Description: SimpleOS Operating System
 A modern operating system with graphical user interface,
 virtual file system, security features and application support.
 .
 Key features:
  * Modern kernel with efficient system calls
  * Virtual File System (VFS) architecture
  * Security system with real-time protection
  * Graphical user interface
  * Built-in applications

